), barrister and author, close friend of Kingsley, or possibly C. T. Simpson, husband of Senior’s sister, Mary Charlotte Mair (b. 1825).); and I had a wholesome walk home, and got no hurt of it. Kingsley, I rather guess, will return upon me tonight “about ten o’clock": I could have well dispensed with a man so useless to me.
